snippet.title: [サテラビュー] 爆笑問題の突撃！ スター パイレーツ 8/25 | Star Pirates 8/25 (Satellaview)
snippet.description:
Coming soon to Satellablog!
http://superfamicom.org/blog

This recording was done with no button inputs except for the "Press A" button prompts at the beginning and end.

IF ANYONE HAS THE ACCOMPANYING AUDIO BROADCAST FOR THIS, PLEASE LET ME KNOW. It is very likely the audio broadcast is necessary to understand what questions are being asked.

Because the ROM's episode is not numbered, I am not certain what episode this is, although based on the documented broadcast dates, it is most likely to be the 2nd episode (Out of 4).

(EDIT: Correction, it is the first episode.)
